Name: caldav_maxdatetime
Type: STRING
Default-Value: 20380119T031407Z
Last-Modified: 2.5.0

The latest date and time accepted by the server (ISO format).  This value
is also used for expanding non-terminating recurrence rules.

Note that increasing this value will require the DAV databases for
calendars to be reconstructed with the :cyrusman:`dav_reconstruct(1)`
utility in order to see its effect on serer-side time-based queries.
